</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.68</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.106em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.106em;">F</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">在许多情况下为“说”</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.21</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.106em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.106em;">F</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">引号后为“说”</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/ur5krelkxzpsbltf56ky" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/bqwxygquntbczjy9goyi 140w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/xu2wkihe055tqwdysd45 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/qwclfqws9wcivsd5gvbv 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/rt6j2mc4efrulio6vxeb 560w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/pyu6gh03oaw0knk5biki 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/gvarzdiisdr8qviueqek 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/osebpggibepszp4ks7xn 980w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/kuuw3b1zsdrbiuo24fxk 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/dedqxxze8l3tgj7hwsrw 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/rcv6vwkcth5i5nvdhxux 1304w"></p><p>我们可以将此计算视为加权逻辑与。输出特征505在A和~B上激活。在 A 是 B 的超集的情况下，这是 B 的补集，例如我有所有水果和所有黄色水果的集合，所以现在我可以找到所有非黄色水果。</p><p> （再次强调，<a href="https://comet-scorpio-0b3.notion.site/More-Examples-ceaefc95cc924afba318dca1da37d4a4">这里</a>有更多示例）</p><h1>稀疏 MLP 特征连接</h1><p>让我们可视化这些损失最严重的 MLP 特征：</p><p>第 5 层：查看线性和 MLP 之间最大损失差异的特征</p><p>（具体为[1.5555、0.0116、0.0052、0.0040、0.0038]）</p><p>所有 5 个功能的激活率都非常高。第一个通常很奇怪（与典型的异常值维度相比），接下来的 4 个大多是奇怪的标记。 <br></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/karjun1tnmpp6qjwzmbd"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/br95vzp1babvnxfqm4ue"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/lgyvhdzu4nwtaqahbysl"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/ujggypvajaaoxsiqxzav"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/htaoeq6cnifh4u8xphvm"></p><p> （作为一般说明：LLM 的最后一层通常非常奇怪！这也出现在调谐透镜纸上，并且被怀旧者假设为扩展的非嵌入矩阵）</p><p>第 4 层：损失差异 [0.0529, 0.0134, 0.0106, 0.0106, 0.0099]</p><p>第一和第三是异常特征。异常值特征的典型特征（根据我的经验）是：</p><p> 1）非常高的激活（这解释了高L2损失）</p><p> 2) 在前几个令牌上激活</p><p>3）在第一个分隔符处激活（例如句点或换行符，我将其表示为“\n”）</p><p> （为什么存在这些？我不知道，文献和理论存在，但超出了本文的范围） </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/v6f5ltmngyyshckpttot"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/gyovzsu4hjndqpdlnqhs"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/qgu4diytowbmgz5uteua"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/isrltm8kiu9lno1fz7zi"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/cfzjxetenumareiyf6zh"></p><p>第 3 层：损失差异 [0.0456, 0.0163, 0.0122, 0.0101, 0.0069]</p><p>第一个和第五个是异常特征</p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/dnl6t83boy0ltkcnltqh"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/fnhuxjirjsl2nutx5fjv"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/xzorozx3elxmgisx3hxg"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/kzkjcaw1cvvvpjtaulrn"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/lcgylzejjs6nlh6vatz3"></p><p>第 2 层：损失差异 [0.3370, 0.3324, 0.2910, 0.1682, 0.1069]</p><p>四个异常值特征</p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/ynbd093akdzpahlenf6m"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/gcsbvca4uc4yjsw71jhc"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/u5lvffwf1myxytieya2w"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/gugve0pcvecth8meebpk"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/laydxbeqld7u2b5co2z6"></p><p>第 1 层：损失差异 [0.1401, 0.0860, 0.0159, 0.0150, 0.0125]</p><p>前两个特征是离群特征</p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/kc0eunsc2areajogzxvm"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/lr9rgsgdpjwgbf0sny1b"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/ppdtkg0uwevck8glq8pi"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/h23mpxmwyx34clcc3iqm"></p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/dfvh6a0gr2z0fw4ee0eh"></p><p>这些特征的具体权重如何？</p><p>因此，MLP 有两组线性权重：W2(relu(W1(x)))。观察 W2，我注意到损失最大的特征有很多大的正权重和负权重。这是前 5 个损失特征（与上面可视化的相同）。对于正权重： <br><br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/yw0uo3yzekejzjpsbdp2" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/qet2futlqzs1s9nvo09w 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/a5o4ul6yeixbopdmv9db 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/gms6oxqd9kkx4g4wfzer 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/ujsxqclveychvswvtqdg 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/sk1zs3qpnhvitaryxznx 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/iwxxitpwduyicaeqd0cw 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/zmcqejzhvy2y9oqdlvio 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/h5bluxefvl5aijafhtts 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/o6vhigs6dbpt3yhwsk0r 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/lbkkmzpulfkeon0qnpak 952w"><br>因此，第 4 层中最高的 loss-diff 特征有 112 个连接权重，且大于 0.1，而中值特征只有 9 个。</p><p>对于负权重： </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/7fxusXdkMNmAhkAfc/svq8lu8bxrmoig6bymyw" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/