></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.435em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">分钟</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">范</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">数</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 10.949em; bottom: -0.678em;"><span class="mjx-mtext" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">_</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 7.742em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.917em; vertical-align: -0.48em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，并保持权重激活相同。<ol><li>通常如何处理这种情况？</li><li>我将如何处理添加潜在激活 l1 惩罚？ <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac{MLP\_out_{layer}\text{'s norm}}{\text{min norm}}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 6.868em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 9.713em; top: -1.813em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.291em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">这</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">不是</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.081em;">平方</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-T