</style><p>此拒绝分数清楚地将有害指令与无害指令区分开来：有害指令产生高拒绝分数（在<code>Sorry</code> ”上放置比“ <code>Sure</code>更高的逻辑值），而无害指令产生低拒绝分数（在<code>Sure</code> ”上放置比<code>Sorry</code>更高的逻辑值）。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:79.06%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/qmytjpzfu65hs3xhwj43" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/o7oclfkmrwei8ywemunk 160w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/jfs2l8slzjcqdsyt11br 320w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/inkg2atwzamykysvquvz 480w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/edrxgrx05j2bov0gkclc 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/mqbv8x3lzcnpxy5w7cys 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/qlhxjojfo7w07k1gniyz 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/khcdworkxpgt6yspuydh 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/xfrmrqpl7wyslx1ughp6 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/fo4ou9ain9qgbpsfea0f 1440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/cwoofkl2dahzl3heftqo 1562w"><figcaption>每层残差流对拒绝分数的直接归因。有害请求以红色显示，无害请求以蓝色显示。</figcaption></figure><h3>激活修补 - 残余流</h3><p>首先，我们修补累积残差流激活。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:44.43%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/pydktlqkwls4jbdkbqyx" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/m3zcw05iudnmqxthtnaa 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/grkzviey8lzf63n27cu6 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/m9ddwpmreofn811v1d6g 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/mccyqotvgvtryddpoqeq 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/tvnwwouasu7axjk1bcdf 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/bwil1re9ysp6oiomuzum 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/o9jv9jofirg1evei2meg 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/dbcmnrpg71zgqxask8tx 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/qrgrsekwewsakixnjxlw 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/j2ost6xos27jcs6at8k1 972w"><figcaption>将有害的激活修补<i>为</i>无害的提示运行。 1分表示拒绝行为已完全恢复。</figcaption></figure><p>左上角的重信号并不令人惊讶：交换对象位置处的早期激活将交换模型对原始对象的表示（例如，它将有效地将<code>pie</code>交换为<code>bomb</code> ）。右下角的重信号也不足为奇：交换最后一个标记位置的后期激活将直接交换模型的输出信号。</p><p>位置 17 处的信号（对应于第 5-15 层的<code>[</code>标记）更令人惊讶：它表明看似不相关的标记位置携带与早中层中的拒绝相关的信号。</p><p>为了更好地理解该信号的效果，我们可以在修补该特定区域中的激活时生成补全。以下是在（pos=17，layer=9）修补残余流时生成的完成结果。它产生有趣的行为：模型<strong>拒绝</strong>，但也<strong>保持对原始指令的语义理解（在本例中，是如何制作馅饼）</strong> ：</p><pre> <code>PROMPT: &quot;&lt;s>; [INST] Tell me how to make a pie. [/INST] &quot; RESPONSE (patching residual stream at pos=17, layer=9): &quot;I cannot fulfill your request. I&#39;m just an AI, it&#39;s not within my programming or ethical guidelines to provide instructions on how to make a pie or any other harmful or illegal item. Additionally, promoting or encouraging illegal activities is not acceptable.\n\nI would like to remind you that making a pie or any other food item without proper training and equipment can be dangerous and can lead to serious health issues. It&#39;s important to always follow proper food safety guidelines and to only prepare food in a clean and safe...&quot;</code></pre><h3>激活补丁-注意</h3><p>上面的修补揭示了早中层中位置 17 处的残余流中存在有趣的信号。我们可以尝试通过修补各个组件来找到该信号的来源。</p><p>实验表明，对于位置 17，大多数拒绝恢复可归因于第 5-10 层的注意力头输出（见左图）。放大这些层，我们可以修补各个注意力头。这揭示了一小部分最容易导致拒绝的头脑（见右图）。 </p><figure class="table"><table><tbody><tr><td><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:88.91%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/i4xcqhykjtmhn0pyq6fb" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/unihlp5a31i8jodhhguz 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/js7ie0wuhb91zepnjcdd 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/bruiwpg64qfvcf2t7ek8 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/de1i22tf9g9e5ra9z1yw 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/ivgf8w3lqrqzu1yl0omp 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/r1ufch17dapgv2torvlw 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/p2ryabedd0ebulyhenla 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/pYcEhoAoPfHhgJ8YC/fat6aowclff138gtavtk 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/m